1.the iot loop

So the basic is to make everything in reality world into simulated in digital world，and then make them communicate through the internet. So the link is like this： 
realworld things--
sensor--
devices--
prototype--
server--
server logic--
prototype--
device--
energy suppliment workers--
do operation work--
sensor--
.
.
.
this is the Iot loop.

